menu "Honor KERNEL STP"

config HN_KERNEL_STP
	tristate "enables Honor KERNEL STP"
	default n
	help
	  This option enables support for Honor kernel stp in kernel space.
	  Honor kernel stp is a security threat perception module at kernel.
	  each source of threat can report the risk info to native throught the kernel stp

config HN_KERNEL_STP_ENG_DEBUG
	bool "Honor KERNEL STP for engineering mode debug"
	depends on HN_KERNEL_STP
	default n
	help
	  This option should only be enabled for engineering mode & debug test.
	  In engineering mode, more debug info can be print for tester.

endmenu
